org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers

Class FormulaCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.util.StringTools
      • org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers.FormulaCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTNodeCompiler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FormulaCompilerLibSBML, FormulaCompilerNoPiecewise, LibSBMLFormulaCompiler

    public class FormulaCompiler
extends StringTools
implements ASTNodeCompiler
    This class creates C-like infix formula Strings that represent the content of ASTNodes. These can be used to save equations in SBML with older than Level 2.
    Since:
    0.8
    Version:
    $Rev: 2091 $
    Author:
    Alexander Dörr, Andreas Dräger

        Description copied from interface: ASTNodeCompiler
